item.name: Hamburger
item.description: Two fresh, hand formed patties hot off the grill and placed on a soft, toasted bun. Choose as many toppings as you want.

item.name: Cheeseburger
item.description: Two slices of Kraft American Cheese melted between two freshly grilled patties on a soft, toasted bun.

item.name: Bacon Burger
item.description: Our regular two-patty burger, layered with four pieces of crispy, sweet applewood-smoked bacon.

item.name: Bacon Cheeseburger
item.description: Two hand-formed patties, grilled to order - with two strips of crispy bacon and two slices of Kraft American Cheese – all on a soft, sesame seed bun.

item.name: Little Hamburger
item.description: One patty instead of two. Top with as many toppings as you choose.

item.name: Little Cheeseburger
item.description: Like our regular cheeseburger, just one grilled to order, hand-crafted patty instead of two.

item.name: Little Bacon Burger
item.description: One freshly made patty grilled to order with two slices of crispy applewood-smoked bacon on top.

item.name: Little Bacon Cheeseburger
item.description: One Five Guys burger patty with crispy, sweet applewood-smoked bacon and Kraft American cheese.

item.name: Kosher Style Hot Dog
item.description: Hebrew National Hotdog, split and grilled lengthwise for a caramelized exterior.

item.name: Cheese Dog
item.description: Hebrew National Hotdog, split and grilled lengthwise with a layer of Kraft American Cheese on top and any of your favorite toppings.

item.name: Bacon Dog
item.description: Hebrew National Hotdog, split and grilled with a layer of crispy, sweet applewood-smoked bacon.

item.name: Bacon Cheese Dog
item.description: Hebrew National Hotdog, split and grilled with a layer of crispy, sweet applewood-smoked bacon.

item.name: Veggie Sandwich
item.description: Freshly grilled onions, mushrooms, and green peppers, layered with lettuce and tomatoes, on a soft toasted bun. Or, start with the bun and build your own from scratch. Not a veggie burger.

item.name: Cheese Veggie Sandwich
item.description: Grilled onions, mushrooms, green peppers with melted American-style cheese, served on a toasted golden bun with lettuce and tomatoes. Plus any of your favorite 16 toppings!

item.name: Grilled Cheese
item.description: Kraft American cheese melted on an inside-out Five Guys bun with any toppings of your choice and grilled until golden brown.

item.name: BLT
item.description: Six whole strips of American smokehouse crispy bacon, two fresh tomato slices, mayo, and hand-torn lettuce on a Five Guys bun.

item.name: Five Guys Style
item.description: Hot, fresh, boardwalk style fries, made to order each and every time. Cut fresh, cooked twice, crispy on the outside and mashed-potato on the inside.

item.name: Cajun Style
item.description: Made to order Five Guys boardwalk style fries, with a heavy dose of Cajun spices. Unsure? Get the seasoning on the side.
